Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.64,0:00:23.33,Dialogue,C,0,0,0,,Today's stage is an inn.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.33,0:00:24.79,Dialogue,C,0,0,0,,A hidden hot spring with a scary legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.15,0:00:26.54,Dialogue,C,0,0,0,,Leftover evidence reveals the hot spring's case!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.96,0:00:28.38,Dialogue,C,0,0,0,,Seeing through to the one and only truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.42,0:00:30.18,Dialogue,C,0,0,0,,I look like a child but have the intellect of an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.19,0:00:32.34,Dialogue,C,0,0,0,,My name is Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.03,0:00:32.13,Signs,C,0,0,0,,Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.93,0:02:42.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Case of the Furisode at the Hidden Hot Spring,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.34,0:02:42.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Part 1!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.16,0:02:49.77,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,Man, this pain in my shoulder has been getting worse lately...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.06,0:02:53.48,Dialogue,DB,0,0,0,,Our hot spring will soothe away that shoulder pain. {changed: "My home's " to "Our"}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.48,0:02:54.65,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,Whoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.32,0:02:58.74,Dialogue,C,0,0,0,,Owner, are these the desserts for tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.26,0:03:02.49,Dialogue,B,0,0,0,,Sorry to disappoint you, but a customer asked me to bring that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.12,0:03:04.83,Dialogue,B,0,0,0,,It seems that she really likes to eat cakes. {changed: "they" to "she"}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.83,0:03:08.12,Dialogue,B,0,0,0,,I heard she's a famous writer. {changed: "they're" to "she's"}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.83,0:03:11.75,Dialogue,S,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, you wanted to eat that, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.75,0:03:13.52,Dialogue,C,0,0,0,,Eh... Well... {changed: "No" to "Well"}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.09,0:03:23.34,Dialogue,W,0,0,0,,Welcome. We've been expecting you for a while now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.72,0:03:26.85,Dialogue,W,0,0,0,,Weren't you cold? Come, please come in. {changed: "Oh, are" to "Weren't"}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.38,0:03:33.02,Dialogue,R,0,0,0,,Ah! These furisodes are so beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.45,0:03:36.98,Dialogue,R,0,0,0,,The garden is so spacious too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.32,0:03:42.07,Dialogue,R,0,0,0,,Hey, isn't that Akechi Eri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, the love story writer? {changed: TL mistake}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.99,0:03:44.91,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,Ow... That hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.91,0:03:46.41,Dialogue,R,0,0,0,,Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.71,0:03:53.35,Dialogue,Y,0,0,0,,Could you be that Detective Mouri? {changed: "Is it possible that you're" to "Could you be that"}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.35,0:03:56.04,Dialogue,Y,0,0,0,,Mouri Kogoro{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.97,0:03:57.96,Dialogue,B,0,0,0,,Mo-Mouri?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.96,0:03:59.34,Dialogue,Y,0,0,0,,I'm right, aren't I?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.01,0:04:02.09,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,Yes. That's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.72,0:04:07.05,Dialogue,B,0,0,0,,It's an honor for me to meet you here, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}. {changed: "I'm really proud to be able to meet Mouri-san here" to current}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.30,0:04:12.54,Dialogue,B,0,0,0,,I'm Nichiuri TV's producer, Bandou Kyouichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.27,0:04:14.85,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.85,0:04:17.27,Dialogue,B,0,0,0,,It's not very comfortable standing and talking here...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.42,0:04:23.78,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,Eh... What are you doing all gathered over here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.78,0:04:27.87,Dialogue Top,B,0,0,0,,Actually, the editor of Daigakukan Publishing and I... {changed: removed "we also invited" to current}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.87,0:04:34.96,Dialogue Top,B,0,0,0,,are discussing scripts Akechi Eri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r} wrote for a new drama airing next spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.58,0:04:41.67,Dialogue,Y,0,0,0,,The drama is about three teenage girls trying to achieve their dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.67,0:04:46.22,Dialogue,Y,0,0,0,,Because of that, I'm interviewing young women who are active in each field.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.09,0:04:53.98,Dialogue,B,0,0,0,,Thus, we've invited three girls who graduated from Yoriko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s alma mater, Oodou University.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.48,0:04:58.94,Dialogue Top,B,0,0,0,,A fashion model active in Paris and New York, Shibazaki Asuka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.94,0:04:59.82,Dialogue,A,0,0,0,,Hi there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.82,0:05:02.11,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,Whoa... Beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.40,0:05:08.53,Dialogue Top,B,0,0,0,,Well, the next girl won the "Best Newcomer Award" in the Kyoto Art Show, oil painter Ansai Ema{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.53,0:05:09.74,Dialogue,E,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.65,0:05:11.91,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,Charming!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.91,0:05:15.04,Dialogue,B,0,0,0,,Last but not least, is the music world's recent
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.04,0:05:18.83,Dialogue,R,0,0,0,,You're the singer and songwriter, Fukatsu Harumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, right? {changed: "Fugatsu" to "Fukatsu"}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.84,0:05:20.50,Dialogue,R,0,0,0,,I'm a big fan of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.50,0:05:23.71,Dialogue,H,0,0,0,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.05,0:05:28.18,Dialogue,A,0,0,0,,Look, you've become quite famous for only having a one-hit wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.18,0:05:32.85,Dialogue,E,0,0,0,,But that'll end soon, just like all the others before you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.64,0:05:40.41,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,The three of you sure have three different personalities. They're also all very beautiful, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.28,0:05:43.44,Dialogue,W,0,0,0,,It's this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.69,0:05:48.86,Dialogue,R,0,0,0,,Ah! There are beautiful furisodes here too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.72,0:05:55.50,Dialogue,R,0,0,0,,Say, why is every room decorated with furisodes and obis?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.50,0:05:58.46,Dialogue,W,0,0,0,,It's because the temple to worship Furisode{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sama{\r} is close by.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.46,0:06:03.59,Dialogue,W,0,0,0,,Every household has them decorated in this way. It's very common. {changed: "family" to "household has them"}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.59,0:06:06.84,Dialogue,R,0,0,0,,Eh? Furisode{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sama{\r}, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.48,0:06:11.47,Dialogue,R,0,0,0,,I'm eager to see your new work, Akechi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.61,0:06:14.39,Dialogue,I,0,0,0,,Please, call me Eri.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.39,0:06:17.77,Dialogue,R,0,0,0,,But... My mother's name is also Eri. {changed: "Your name is pronounced the same way as my mother's" to current}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.77,0:06:20.85,Dialogue,R,0,0,0,,And it feels weird saying "Eri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}." {changed: added "And"}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.87,0:06:22.73,Dialogue,R,0,0,0,,They're written differently, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.73,0:06:26.53,Dialogue,I,0,0,0,,I know what you mean. When people call me "Akechi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r},"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.57,0:06:30.07,Dialogue,I,0,0,0,,it sounds like a detective investigating, and it makes me feel embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.14,0:06:35.58,Dialogue,R,0,0,0,,I heard that a god called Furisode{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sama{\r} is worshiped around here. {changed: "I heard that there's a god called Furisode-sama nearby." to current}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.89,0:06:37.45,Dialogue,I,0,0,0,,Yeah... However,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.45,0:06:41.42,Dialogue,I,0,0,0,,there's a dark side to Furisode{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sama{\r} known as Furisode-Hannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.22,0:06:43.92,Dialogue,C,0,0,0,,Furisode-Hannya?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.26,0:06:46.63,Dialogue,I,0,0,0,,It's from an old folk legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.63,0:06:53.18,Dialogue,I,0,0,0,,A long time ago, a woman named Ohana lived in this village. She was kind and hardworking.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.18,0:06:57.39,Dialogue,I,0,0,0,,One day, Ohana found a wounded samurai and nursed him back to health.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.89,0:07:02.15,Dialogue,I,0,0,0,,In return, he gave her many beautiful furisodes and obis.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.60,0:07:07.15,Dialogue,I,0,0,0,,Seeing that, the sisters became envious and accused her of slander.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.65,0:07:11.26,Dialogue,I,0,0,0,,They called the magistrates to take away her furisodes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.14,0:07:19.45,Dialogue,I,0,0,0,,The night of Ohana's execution, the sisters stole her furisodes and obis.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.45,0:07:22.29,Dialogue,I,0,0,0,,While they were celebrating, a cold breeze blew the lights out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.54,0:07:28.30,Dialogue,I,0,0,0,,Awakened by the miserable screams, the rest of the family ran to see what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.30,0:07:31.76,Dialogue,I,0,0,0,,The furisodes were spread out across the floor, and the younger sister had stopped breathing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.70,0:07:37.36,Dialogue,I,0,0,0,,The elder sister was found dead in the garden pond, entangled by the obis.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.23,0:07:41.02,Dialogue,I,0,0,0,,After that, the villagers all knew about Ohana's deep hatred,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.02,0:07:43.98,Dialogue,I,0,0,0,,so they made a shrine to be the village's protector.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.52,0:07:48.02,Dialogue,I,0,0,0,,Thus, Furisode{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sama{\r} could be worshiped anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.39,0:07:52.99,Dialogue,I,0,0,0,,That hotel is also known as "Furisode{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sama{\r}'s Mansion."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.57,0:07:55.66,Dialogue,R,0,0,0,,You seem to know a lot about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.66,0:08:00.00,Dialogue,I,0,0,0,,Yes... I stay in that hotel quite frequently and collect information for my writing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.57,0:08:04.50,Dialogue,C,0,0,0,,H-Hey, isn't that Harumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.93,0:08:05.93,Dialogue,R,0,0,0,,That's her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.93,0:08:06.90,Dialogue,R,0,0,0,,Harumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.05,0:08:14.05,Dialogue,H,0,0,0,,This tree is called "Furisode Sakura." It's nearly 500 years old now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.07,0:08:18.01,Dialogue,H,0,0,0,,In the spring, the tree's branches will be covered in sakura.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.48,0:08:21.52,Dialogue,H,0,0,0,,It'll look just like a beautiful furisode.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.20,0:08:24.68,Dialogue,R,0,0,0,,Harumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, are you familiar with this village as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.68,0:08:25.77,Dialogue,H,0,0,0,,Huh? No.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.25,0:08:29.65,Dialogue,H,0,0,0,,It's because my senpai in the university liked sakura a lot,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.65,0:08:32.78,Dialogue,H,0,0,0,,and she told me about this sakura tree here. {changed: From "They're the ones who told me the story of this tree" to current}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.28,0:08:36.03,Dialogue,H,0,0,0,,I just remembered that, so I came here to see it for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.57,0:08:40.27,Dialogue,C,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.27,0:08:42.20,Dialogue,C,0,0,0,,What's that shrine for?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.04,0:08:47.13,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,Now, look! You little brat, you can't keep running off somewhere all the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.96,0:08:49.04,Dialogue,I,0,0,0,,That's the shrine to pay tribute to Furisode.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.42,0:08:50.96,Thoughts,C,0,0,0,,{\be10}Tribute to Furisode?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.25,0:08:54.97,Dialogue,I,0,0,0,,Furisode{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sama{\r} is also the god of vengeance.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.99,0:08:55.97,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,V-Vengeance?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.50,0:08:59.46,Dialogue,I,0,0,0,,According to the legend, those who wear furisode come to pay tribute at midnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.46,0:09:02.14,Dialogue,I,0,0,0,,They're unable to get revenge with their current strength,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.14,0:09:06.23,Dialogue,I,0,0,0,,so Furisode{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sama{\r} will get revenge on their behalf.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.35,0:09:12.23,Dialogue,I,0,0,0,,The Chiyogami dolls in it were contributed by those who paid visits to Furisode{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sama{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.99,0:09:15.70,Dialogue,H,0,0,0,,There are some new dolls here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.29,0:09:17.70,Dialogue,R,0,0,0,,Two new ones!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.70,0:09:19.95,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,What? What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.90,0:09:24.75,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,This means that someone has paid tribute to Furisode.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.16,0:09:29.00,Dialogue,I,0,0,0,,It means they have two people they want to get revenge on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.49,0:09:32.75,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,No matter what, it's just a practical joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.35,0:09:35.75,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,Don't take it so seriously, Ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.69,0:09:39.93,Dialogue,C,0,0,0,,Say, that's not the shrine, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.14,0:09:44.60,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,Don't be annoying. It's just the guest room.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.89,0:09:47.94,Dialogue,I,0,0,0,,There {\i1}is{\i0} a place there to worship Furisode{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sama{\r}, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.94,0:09:51.86,Dialogue,R,0,0,0,,C-C-Could there be even more Chiyogami dolls inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.88,0:09:53.61,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,H-How could that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.82,0:09:58.24,Dialogue,R,0,0,0,,But I'm worried about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.25,0:10:01.74,Dialogue,R,0,0,0,,Come on, Dad. Let's go have a look at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.01,0:10:02.81,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,You mean me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.81,0:10:03.62,Dialogue,R,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.01,0:10:09.62,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,Really, that Ran...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.92,0:10:13.50,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,How could there be dolls over here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.05,0:10:15.63,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,See? I was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.89,0:10:16.97,Dialogue,C,0,0,0,,Yeah... {changed: "Maybe..." to current}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.50,0:10:18.99,Dialogue,C,0,0,0,,There's nothing else here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.99,0:10:20.64,Dialogue,R,0,0,0,,Really?! That's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.39,0:10:27.48,Dialogue,R,0,0,0,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.02,0:10:30.15,Dialogue,R,0,0,0,,It's just like the picture in the pamphlet! {changed: "advertisement" to "pamphlet"}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.48,0:10:36.16,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,This is paradise; it's paradise!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.82,0:10:39.16,Dialogue,C,0,0,0,,"This is paradise; it's paradise."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.41,0:10:43.16,Dialogue,R,0,0,0,,How beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.73,0:10:45.66,Dialogue,ALL,0,0,0,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.06,0:10:50.34,Dialogue,B,0,0,0,,Everyone, for being able to interview you all these past four days,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.34,0:10:52.50,Dialogue,B,0,0,0,,I want to thank you all so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.88,0:10:57.96,Dialogue,E,0,0,0,,Eri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, please let me be the character who has the most screen time in the drama.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.97,0:11:01.47,Dialogue,I,0,0,0,,Now, now. I haven't even decided on how the story will go yet. {changed: "the ending to the storyline" to "how the story will go"}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.97,0:11:05.06,Dialogue,E,0,0,0,,That's why I'm asking you now. {changed: "I have to mention it to you early on" to "I'm asking you now"}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.51,0:11:07.47,Dialogue,Y,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, Bandou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.04,0:11:11.69,Dialogue,Y,0,0,0,,Just let Harumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} write the theme song!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.03,0:11:14.34,Dialogue,B,0,0,0,,Ah... That's a good idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.34,0:11:15.94,Dialogue,B,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.43,0:11:19.72,Dialogue,A,0,0,0,,If her popularity keeps up, that is.{changed: From "As long as it's able to be as popular as usual, it's fine." to current}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.34,0:11:25.04,Dialogue,R,0,0,0,,This is tasty, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.04,0:11:25.58,Dialogue,C,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.33,0:11:32.42,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,What? Is it empty before I even opened it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.80,0:11:34.38,Thoughts,C,0,0,0,,{\be10}How could that be possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.83,0:11:37.75,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}. Get me another bottle.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.46,0:11:43.46,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,Just one. Just one bottle's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.46,0:11:47.81,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,Then I won't drink anymore, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.81,0:11:49.31,Dialogue,R,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.04,0:11:54.91,Dialogue,R,0,0,0,,Come on. Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, you're tricky.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.91,0:11:57.40,Dialogue,H,0,0,0,,Hey, is now a good time?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.40,0:11:58.40,Dialogue,R,0,0,0,,Yes, please come in!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.83,0:12:01.40,Dialogue,R,0,0,0,,Oh, Harumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.82,0:12:05.41,Dialogue,H,0,0,0,,Actually, I wanted to find Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} to discuss something with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.07,0:12:07.41,Dialogue,R,0,0,0,,D-Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.52,0:12:10.54,Dialogue,R,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.35,0:12:12.55,Thoughts,C,0,0,0,,{\be10}Discuss?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.38,0:12:18.80,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,Huh? What's going on? I thought something happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.52,0:12:27.43,Dialogue,H,0,0,0,,Five years ago, when I was a third-year in the university,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.18,0:12:30.77,Dialogue,H,0,0,0,,an illegal drug became popular on campus.{changed: from "it was becoming popular to restrict drugs on campus." to current}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.77,0:12:32.68,Dialogue,H,0,0,0,,Searching for the seller of all those drugs,{changed: from "As the head of the program was investigating secret transactions and such," to current}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.71,0:12:34.77,Dialogue,H,0,0,0,,investigators found the name of a girl.{changed: from "a girl was caught." to current}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.56,0:12:38.86,Dialogue,H,0,0,0,,She denied it, but drugs were found inside her locker.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.86,0:12:41.52,Dialogue,H,0,0,0,,So, in order to prove her innocence,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.53,0:12:47.28,Dialogue,H,0,0,0,,she jumped from the university's rooftop and died.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.32,0:12:56.96,Dialogue,H,0,0,0,,Her name is Suzuka Sakurako{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, and she was the senpai who loved sakura under the Furisode tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.96,0:13:02.17,Dialogue,H,0,0,0,,There's no way the senpai I knew could have secretly been a drug dealer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.83,0:13:04.67,Dialogue,H,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.67,0:13:08.14,Dialogue,H,0,0,0,,One more time. Investigate this case one more time, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.94,0:13:12.47,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,It's been five years already...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.89,0:13:18.35,Dialogue,H,0,0,0,,Actually, there was a rumor mentioning another culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.65,0:13:23.57,Dialogue,H,0,0,0,,However, those students... They... are the children of a powerful family.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.57,0:13:26.82,Dialogue,H,0,0,0,,Nobody in school dares to speak badly of these girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.13,0:13:28.70,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,G-Girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.40,0:13:32.95,Dialogue,H,0,0,0,,Shibazaki Asuka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and Anzai Ema{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.95,0:13:35.71,Dialogue,H,0,0,0,,Asuka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} is the daughter of the senator Shibazaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.34,0:13:40.46,Dialogue,H,0,0,0,,Ema{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} is the daughter of the Anzai Group's president.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.13,0:13:45.66,Dialogue,H,0,0,0,,These two were always fighting with Sakurako{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, who had a strong sense of justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.66,0:13:47.68,Dialogue,H,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, please look into this!{changed: from "help with this!" to "look into this!"}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.02,0:13:51.51,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.51,0:13:53.68,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,I'll definitely try my best to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.64,0:13:56.35,Dialogue,H,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.81,0:13:59.73,Dialogue,R,0,0,0,,You must really like that senpai, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.28,0:14:03.54,Dialogue,H,0,0,0,,I lost my parents when I was little.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.54,0:14:05.57,Dialogue,H,0,0,0,,My aunt and uncle brought me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.99,0:14:10.20,Dialogue,H,0,0,0,,Sakurako{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s parents also died, in a fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.20,0:14:12.45,Dialogue,H,0,0,0,,So, we got along very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.76,0:14:28.47,Dialogue,I,0,0,0,,Oh? You're going to bathe in the hot spring?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.26,0:14:31.29,Dialogue,R,0,0,0,,Are you going to take a bath in the hot spring too, Eri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.29,0:14:33.76,Dialogue,R,0,0,0,,Yes. It's a little cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.76,0:14:36.22,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,How about we go for a drink afterwards?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.71,0:14:38.29,Dialogue,I,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.29,0:14:40.44,Dialogue,I,0,0,0,,I still have some work I need to get done.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.69,0:14:43.44,Dialogue,C,0,0,0,,See you later then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.24,0:14:47.40,Dialogue,R,0,0,0,,Eh? Someone already reserved it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.40,0:14:48.28,Dialogue,H,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.99,0:14:53.57,Dialogue,H,0,0,0,,The door's locked.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.57,0:14:56.69,Dialogue,H,0,0,0,,We have no choice then. We have to wait another half hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.70,0:14:58.50,Dialogue,H,0,0,0,,In the meantime, let's go play ping-pong.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.00,0:15:00.50,Dialogue,R,0,0,0,,Yeah, let's do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.11,0:15:08.01,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,They sound really busy in the next room. {changed: "look" to "sound"}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.35,0:15:10.80,Thoughts,C,0,0,0,,{\be10}What're Ran and the others doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.42,0:15:13.46,Dialogue,R,0,0,0,,I'm ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.43,0:15:15.47,Dialogue,H,0,0,0,,Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.64,0:15:21.45,Dialogue,C,0,0,0,,Huh? You finished your bath already?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.45,0:15:24.15,Dialogue,R,0,0,0,,Nope. We haven't taken it yet... {changed: "I" to "We"}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.15,0:15:26.16,Dialogue,R,0,0,0,,because the bath was being reserved for someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.00,0:15:30.60,Dialogue,C,0,0,0,,Oh? You're wearing glasses, Harumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.12,0:15:33.18,Dialogue,H,0,0,0,,I forgot to bring my contacts,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.19,0:15:34.91,Dialogue,H,0,0,0,,so I just put these on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.80,0:15:45.79,Dialogue,R,0,0,0,,It's 11:30pm now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.44,0:15:48.84,Dialogue,R,0,0,0,,The bath was only rented until 11pm, and it's past that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.84,0:15:51.01,Dialogue,H,0,0,0,,Yeah, let's go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.02,0:15:56.37,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,Huh? Wh-Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.37,0:15:57.67,Dialogue,C,0,0,0,,Women's hot spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.99,0:16:00.02,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.68,0:16:03.27,Dialogue,R,0,0,0,,Huh? They're still in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.33,0:16:05.77,Dialogue,R,0,0,0,,It's really locked up tight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.18,0:16:08.80,Dialogue,R,0,0,0,,What is this thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.80,0:16:11.53,Dialogue,H,0,0,0,,That wasn't here earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.32,0:16:16.82,Dialogue,R,0,0,0,,It feels a little cold in my hands. Gives me the chills.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.33,0:16:21.66,Dialogue,R,0,0,0,,What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.89,0:16:23.12,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,Wh-What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.45,0:16:24.64,Thoughts,C,0,0,0,,{\be10}Furisode-Hannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.95,0:16:32.01,Dialogue,C,0,0,0,,Uncle, break down the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.69,0:16:34.70,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,Stay back!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.04,0:16:45.52,Dialogue,R,0,0,0,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.54,0:16:48.40,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,Alcohol's worn off now...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.82,0:16:51.43,Dialogue,H,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, is anyone there?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.19,0:16:54.40,Dialogue,C,0,0,0,,Yes, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.97,0:17:02.04,Dialogue,R,0,0,0,,Asuka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.71,0:17:06.18,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,Asuka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.13,0:17:09.67,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,Asuka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.63,0:17:13.08,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,Too late. She's been stabbed in her chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.62,0:17:16.00,Thoughts,C,0,0,0,,{\be10}The Legend of Furisode-Hannya...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.00,0:17:16.81,Thoughts,C,0,0,0,,{\be10}Don't tell me that...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.31,0:17:20.18,Dialogue,R,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, where are you going?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.51,0:17:22.85,Thoughts,C,0,0,0,,{\be10}In the legend, both sisters were killed...{changed: from "The legend said that all the sisters were killed..." to current}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.43,0:17:29.40,Dialogue,Y,0,0,0,,Huh? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.22,0:17:31.27,Dialogue,R,0,0,0,,Asuka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.51,0:17:33.28,Dialogue,B,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.48,0:17:35.81,Dialogue,H,0,0,0,,Asuka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was... in the bath... {changed: "killed in the hot spring!" to current}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.82,0:17:38.24,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,She's been murdered by someone!{changed: from "I'm going to find out who did this!" to current}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.71,0:17:40.17,Dialogue,Y,0,0,0,,Wh-What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.17,0:17:41.16,Dialogue,I,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.74,0:17:42.37,Dialogue,C,0,0,0,,Where's Ema{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.95,0:17:46.25,Dialogue,Y,0,0,0,,If I remember correctly, she went that way about an hour ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.00,0:17:56.72,Thoughts,C,0,0,0,,{\be10}Footprints from Ema{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10}'s boots...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.30,0:18:02.22,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,Did she run over that way?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.22,0:18:04.35,Dialogue,C,0,0,0,,Uncle, be careful not to step on these tracks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.35,0:18:08.06,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,Of course! What do you think I am, an amateur or something? {Yes...}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.83,0:18:26.33,Thoughts,C,0,0,0,,{\be10}Just as I thought, is this Furisode-Hannya?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.33,0:18:29.04,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,It's the same situation here. Her chest was stabbed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.75,0:18:33.04,Thoughts,C,0,0,0,,{\be10}There are only Ema{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10}'s footprints outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.80,0:18:37.55,Thoughts,C,0,0,0,,{\be10}This means that this is a secret room which was concealed by the heavy snowfall.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.18,0:18:40.05,Dialogue,P,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.47,0:18:43.35,Dialogue,P,0,0,0,,I was sent to help Detective Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.68,0:18:45.00,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.91,0:18:49.06,Dialogue,P,0,0,0,,I'm the patrolman in this village, Omura.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.59,0:18:50.65,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,Have you contacted the main police station?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.65,0:18:53.06,Dialogue,P,0,0,0,,Yes. I called them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.09,0:18:57.49,Dialogue,P,0,0,0,,But because of the heavy snow, the earliest they can arrive is tomorrow morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.19,0:18:59.74,Thoughts,C,0,0,0,,{\be10}Tomorrow morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.02,0:19:01.38,Thoughts,M,0,0,0,,{\be10}No choice then...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.38,0:19:04.90,Thoughts,M,0,0,0,,{\be10}It's up to us to search and protect the crime scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.90,0:19:09.18,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,Landlady, bring me ten large towels.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.75,0:19:10.50,Dialogue,W,0,0,0,,S-Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.80,0:19:14.63,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,Everyone, please wait in the living room.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.63,0:19:15.25,Dialogue,ALL,0,0,0,,S-Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.07,0:19:17.76,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,A little slower, Omura{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.50,0:19:24.68,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,Right. Cover the footprints lightly. A little lower...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.40,0:19:29.63,Thoughts,C,0,0,0,,{\be10}If you walk along this route after the long corridor, you'd reach the back door.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.11,0:19:35.15,Thoughts,C,0,0,0,,{\be10}However, there isn't a single footprint.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.89,0:19:40.53,Thoughts,C,0,0,0,,{\be10}Eh... That's strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.74,0:19:45.16,Thoughts,C,0,0,0,,{\be10}What is it? Something's just not right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.16,0:19:49.42,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,Hey! The snow will cover the footprints if you open that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.21,0:19:53.37,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,All of you are here...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.07,0:19:57.21,Dialogue,Y,0,0,0,,Oh, that. Eri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r} told us that we needed to sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.21,0:19:59.49,Dialogue,B,0,0,0,,Have you figured anything out yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.87,0:20:05.72,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,Yoriko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, Ema{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} passed by this lobby around 10:30pm, right? {changed: "the living room" to "this lobby"}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.12,0:20:08.04,Dialogue,Y,0,0,0,,Yes. That's correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.04,0:20:10.35,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,Did you see anyone else walk by?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.35,0:20:11.73,Dialogue,Y,0,0,0,,No, no one else.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.35,0:20:15.61,Dialogue,P,0,0,0,,Well, this could be troublesome now...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.91,0:20:18.02,Dialogue,B,0,0,0,,Wh-What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.80,0:20:22.78,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,First, the shrine where Ema{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was killed:
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.78,0:20:27.74,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,Snow revealed that only Ema{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s footprints were there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.37,0:20:30.24,Dialogue,Y,0,0,0,,So then, Ema{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} committed suicide?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.24,0:20:34.99,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,No. No trace of a weapon was discovered at the crime scene. {changed: "The crime scenes don't have any similarities, such as weapons, to connect them." to current}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.99,0:20:36.25,Dialogue,R,0,0,0,,That can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.59,0:20:40.35,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,Next is the hot spring where Asuka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was killed:
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.35,0:20:44.59,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,You'd also need to pass by the recreation area to get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.59,0:20:48.60,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,However, we were there since 10:30pm.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.60,0:20:50.60,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,If someone walked by, we'd know about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.60,0:20:53.70,Dialogue,B,0,0,0,,What if someone were to climb from the mountain valley to the cliff and got in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.70,0:20:57.99,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,I checked the cliff. It didn't have any suspicious traces.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.99,0:21:02.49,Dialogue,B,0,0,0,,This means Asuka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} might've been killed before 10:30pm.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.49,0:21:07.24,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,There was a knife and a stun gun found at the bottom of the hot spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.25,0:21:11.26,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,The culprit most likely used the stun gun to make the victim faint,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.26,0:21:13.00,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,then they killed her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.45,0:21:16.98,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,The knife's hilt is decorated with a shell-like design.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.98,0:21:18.75,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,I'll need to confirm this with the landlady, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.04,0:21:21.96,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,I heard that it's the holy knife that was donated as part of the shrine in the garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.72,0:21:23.97,Dialogue,H,0,0,0,,The holy knife...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.97,0:21:25.56,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,One more thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.56,0:21:28.72,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,Ema{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s bandana was found in the open-air hot spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.22,0:21:31.93,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,The bandana had blood stains on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.95,0:21:33.28,Dialogue,R,0,0,0,,What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.28,0:21:35.48,Dialogue,B,0,0,0,,That... In short...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.48,0:21:40.43,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,In short, both of them were killed with the same knife.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.44,0:21:44.49,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,So, we know that the culprit killed Ema{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} first, then went after Asuka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.03,0:21:48.86,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,Also, Ema{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} had to have still been alive before 10:30pm,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.86,0:21:51.99,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,since Asuka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} hadn't been killed before that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.45,0:21:55.20,Dialogue,I,0,0,0,,How did the culprit get into the hot spring, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.57,0:21:59.63,Dialogue,Y,0,0,0,,There weren't any footprints around the shrine in the garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.63,0:22:03.55,Dialogue,B,0,0,0,,It wasn't a ghost, so how could this happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.57,0:22:04.71,Dialogue,I,0,0,0,,It's the curse!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.78,0:22:07.68,Dialogue,I,0,0,0,,Furisode-Hannya's curse!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.68,0:22:09.59,Dialogue,B,0,0,0,,Wh-What do you mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.14,0:22:11.92,Dialogue,H,0,0,0,,We saw them! {changed: "that" to "them"}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.92,0:22:16.56,Dialogue,H,0,0,0,,There were two new Furisode dolls in the Holy Mansion's shrine!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.44,0:22:21.07,Dialogue,H,0,0,0,,Asuka and Ema were killed by Furisode-Hannya's curse!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.07,0:22:23.40,Dialogue,R,0,0,0,,H-How could this happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.70,0:22:27.28,Thoughts,C,0,0,0,,{\be10}That kind of curse definitely doesn't exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.03,0:22:32.33,Thoughts,C,0,0,0,,{\be10}However, what kind of trick did the culprit use?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.41,0:24:01.83,Dialogue,C,0,0,0,,They visited Furisode!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.83,0:24:05.71,Dialogue,C,0,0,0,,Sakurako{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} visited Furisode and wanted revenge on those two people!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.50,0:24:09.17,Thoughts,C,0,0,0,,{\be10}So, that's how it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.38,0:24:14.60,Dialogue,C,0,0,0,,Exactly. That's why... That's why Senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.58,0:24:20.63,Dialogue,C,0,0,0,,Wait! Why are your socks all wet?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.72,0:24:24.02,Dialogue,C,0,0,0,,Hold on. Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.60,0:24:29.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan: Case of the Furisode at the Hidden Hot Spring, Part 2!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.05,0:24:33.52,Dialogue,C,0,0,0,,Next Conan's Hint!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.52,0:24:34.37,Dialogue,C,0,0,0,,Obi.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.32,0:24:36.87,Dialogue Top,C,0,0,0,,Do you have an obi, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.87,0:24:38.32,Dialogue Top,C,0,0,0,,I have a black belt in karate.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.32,0:24:40.04,Dialogue Top,C,0,0,0,,That's not quite the same...
